      </style></div><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center lg:mt-28 mb-12"><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start"><img src="/car-images/mitsubishi-hero.jpg" alt="Used Mitsubishi auto parts hero image" class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-xl"/></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center"><h3 class="font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3 text-white">Choose Us to Revamp Your Mitsubishi Requirements</h3><p class="text-[18px] leading-[30px] text-[#cecece]">Mitsubishi is known for producing high-performance, fuel-efficient, and technologically advanced vehicles. The first Mitsubishi Model A, introduced in 1917, marked the beginning of a strong legacy admired by many around the world.</p></div></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-14"><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Mitsubishi History</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>1970s–1980s: Launch of iconic models such as Mitsubishi Lancer and Pajero.</li><li>1990: Major influence in the World Rally Championships with the evolution of Lancer.</li><li>2000s–Present: Introduction and expansion of hybrid vehicles like Mitsubishi Outlander.</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Why Mitsubishi Is Favored by Enthusiasts</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Durability: Built to last long with an exceptional driving experience.</li><li>Off-Road Performance: All-terrain capability in models like Pajero and Outlander.</li><li>Fuel Efficiency: Outstanding mileage in compact and hybrid models.</li><li>Affordability: Premium features at cost-effective prices.</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Technology and Engine Performance</h3><div class="mt-6"><h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Engine Types</h4><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 text-[#cecece]"><li>2.0L &amp; 2.4L MIVEC Engines – Smooth performance found in Lancer, Outlander, and Eclipse Cross.</li><li>4B11 Turbocharged Engine – High horsepower and torque for Lancer Evolution.</li><li>3.0L V6 SOHC Engine – Strong towing power, seen in Pajero and Montero.</li><li>1.2L &amp; 1.5L DOHC Engine – Fuel-efficient compact engines in Mitsubishi Mirage.</li><li>Hybrid Technology – Plug-in hybrid system in the Mitsubishi Outlander.</li></ul></div><div class="mt-6"><h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Transmission Types</h4><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 text-[#cecece]"><li>CVT (Continuously Variable Transmission) – Seamless acceleration.</li><li>5-Speed &amp; 6-Speed Manual Transmissions – Built for performance and off-road models.</li><li>INVECS-II / INVECS-III Automatic Transmissions – Adaptive shift control technology.</li><li>Super All-Wheel Control (S-AWC) – Advanced AWD system for Lancer Evolution &amp; Outlander.</li></ul></div></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Formation of Designs</h3><div class="mt-6"></div><div class="mt-6"></div></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Why Buy Used Mitsubishi Auto Parts at PARTSCENTRAL?</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">PARTSCENTRAL maintains its reputation by offering rigorously inspected Mitsubishi OEM parts that meet industry standards.</p><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Extensive inventory of Mitsubishi Outlander, Eclipse, Lancer, Mirage, Fuso, and more.</li><li>Budget-friendly, high-quality used OEM Mitsubishi components.</li><li>Parts are checked thoroughly for reliability and performance.</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Is Shipping Available for Mitsubishi Car Parts?</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">PARTSCENTRAL provides free shipping to all business addresses and delivers Mitsubishi parts across the United States.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">How PARTSCENTRAL Stands Apart</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>30-day warranty on small parts, 90-day warranty on engines &amp; transmissions.</li><li>Financing options to make purchases flexible and affordable.</li><li>Nationwide shipping with swift delivery.</li><li>24/7 customer support for all Mitsubishi requirements.</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Customer Testimonials</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>“Finding parts for my Mitsubishi Lancer was tough until PARTSCENTRAL helped me find the perfect fit!” – John, California</li><li>“Ordered a side mirror and fender — arrived within 48 hours!” – Emma, Arizona</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Trust PARTSCENTRAL for Used Mitsubishi Auto Parts</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Get a quote for Mitsubishi parts by submitting your model, year, and VIN on our website. Our support team responds quickly to assist with all your needs.</p><p class="mt-4 font-bold text-white">Call us at 877-982-7774 — available 365 days a year, round-the-clock.</p></div></div><div class="w-full mt-20 py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-8  bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-center rounded-2xl"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Find Quality <!-- -->Buy Used Mitsubishi Auto Parts at PARTSCENTRAL<!-- --> Parts Today?</h2><p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">Get fast pricing, expert guidance, and nationwide delivery on quality used auto parts for your <!-- -->Buy Used Mitsubishi Auto Parts at PARTSCENTRAL<!-- -->.</p><a href="/" class="inline-block  bg-[#00A3FF]  text-white px-7 sm:px-9 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,163,255,0.45)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,163,255,0.7)